---
import MainLayout from '../../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout
  title="Mini Forklift Design and Assembly"
  description="Designed and assembled a functional mini forklift."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Projects</p>

    <h1>Mini Forklift Design and Assembly</h1>

    <p class="intro">
      Designed and assembled a functional mini forklift while validating
      performance through engineering calculations.
    </p>

    <img
      src="/images/projects/mini-forklift.jpg"
      alt="Mini Forklift Design and Assembly"
    />
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Overview</h2>

    <p>
      The project focused on designing and assembling a compact forklift while
      ensuring the lift mechanism met performance requirements.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Process</h2>

    <p>
      Mechanical calculations for torque, gear ratios, and load capacity were
      performed to validate the design before assembly and testing.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Tools Used</h2>

    <p>SOLIDWORKS • MATLAB • Mechanical Design</p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  img {
    width: 100%;
    border-radius: 24px;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  section + section {
    margin-top: 4rem;
  }

  .hero {
    max-width: 48rem;
  }

  .intro {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
  }
</style>